Package com.g1.mychess.player.dto

Class PlayerProfileDTO

java.lang.Object
com.g1.mychess.player.dto.PlayerProfileDTO
public class PlayerProfileDTO extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a player's profile details. This class encapsulates the player's information such as personal details, chess ratings, total wins/losses/draws, and the visibility of their profile.

      Parameters:
      playerId - the unique identifier for the player
      username - the username of the player
      fullName - the full name of the player
      bio - the biography or description of the player
      avatarUrl - the URL of the player's avatar image
      gender - the gender of the player
      country - the country of the player
      region - the region of the player
      city - the city of the player
      birthDate - the birth date of the player
      rank - the custom chess rank of the player
      glickoRating - the Glicko rating of the player
      ratingDeviation - the Glicko rating deviation of the player
      volatility - the volatility of the player's Glicko rating
      totalWins - the total number of wins for the player
      totalLosses - the total number of losses for the player
      totalDraws - the total number of draws for the player
      isPublic - whether the player's profile is public
      age - the age of the player
